							<a name="City of Mist Follow up">City of Mist Follow up
					</td>
					<td align="right">
						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Monday, February&nbsp;26
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							Many thanks to all of those who atteneded our raid on the City
					of Mist this past Saturday. The raid went excellently. After
					we teamed up with Amici together we were able to take out
					Rak'Ashiir and got a Runed Ornate Blade! Two Jade Reavers and
					a Mace of Shadowed Souls droped as well! There were no wipe outs
					and very few deaths! Check back soon for more news on the City
					of Mist Raid.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
						</div>
					</td>
				</tr>
