						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Friday, February&nbsp;16
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							Boisvert will be gone this coming weekend to return monday.
					A few page layout and little things will be or already have been
					changed as well. The applications forum you might have noticed
					is locked. Instead of posting in a forum open to the public if you
					wish to apply to The Hidden please send an email to <a
					href="ug_mug@yahoo.com">ug_mug@yahoo.com</a> at the present time
					with the appropriate information. Boisvert will then post in the
					members only section where any prospective members may be
					sponsored. From the time that a person is sponsored there shall
					be one week of voting at the maximum. In an effort to get back
					to prospective members any votes cast by the end of this week
					shall be counted. So members make sure to keep checking the
					members only section to get your vote in. For the layout as well
					some people have expressed some confusion in the board layout.
					The follow three links are the most important ones that should be
					checked as often as possible: <a
					href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fhiddenfrm0">General</a>, <a
					href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fhiddenfrm1">Events</a>, <a
					href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fhiddenfrm3">Members Only</a>.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
						</div>
