							<a name="Paw Falls">Paw Falls
					</td>
					<td align="right">
						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Saturday, February&nbsp;3
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							Last night The Hidden arrived at Paw and brought it to the
					ground. Even when Kurrpok Splitpaw attempted to flee we chased
					him down and the train he created we destroyed all comers.
					Congratulations to Mitivo and Mardia for aquiring Kurrpok's Ruby
					Pendant for the Jeweled Skull Quest. This was the last piece
					Mitivo needed. Congratulations to Mardia as well for getting her
					summon corpse spell. Time for everyone to put a coffin in the
					bank. One named Gnoll, Tesch Val Deval'Nmak, also dared to show
					his face but only left us with some White Hellbore.<br><br>

					While Innoruuk.com is under this transitional period The Hidden's
					page might also experience some difficultys. In that event our
					board which is hosted by someone else can be found at <a
					href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/bhidden">
					http://pub42.ezboard.com/bhidden</a>. Boisvert can also be
					contacted at his alternative email address <a
					href="mailto:ug_mug@yahoo.com">ug_mug@yahoo.com</a>. Hopefully
					these downtime problems will be fixed in the near future.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
